name: Freedom to Play God - Sean.Graham.Digital
description: 20" x 20" 1-Bit depth bitmap. A monstrous lump generated in GANBreeder but likely scooped from the infernal pit of the Metaverse. The image was then reduced to a halftone bitmap to remove pixelation and make an interesting piece of printable CryptoArt. Zoom in. @studiosometimes
